title: [Sylvarraend Road, Boulder]
description: From the top of the smooth boulder, the view of Ta'Illistim's famed spires is breathtaking.  Reaching towards the sky as if they were attempting to pluck the stars from the heavens, the lapis tiles glitter in the moonlight.

From the top of the smooth boulder, the view of Ta'Illistim's famed spires is breathtaking.  Reaching towards the sky as if they were attempting to pluck the stars from the heavens, the lapis tiles glitter in the day's light.
